    <note>Zhao(1) Fu(4) [26308] His wife, born Cui(1), was first married to a Daming resident, Sun(1) Guang, who died after she had given birth to two sons. She then traveled to Kaifeng and relied on her elder sister for support. When the latter died, she remarried Zhao(1) Fu(4), who was a member of either the Eastern or Western branches of the Gaomi Zhao(2) (see documentation for Zhao(1) Cuizhong [25203]). She had three sons by Fu(4), who she married at age 31 and died at age 57. Fu(4) died two years after she. Zheng Xie, WJ, 22.5a-56a (wife).</note>
